title: Turkey claims to break Guinness world record for largest baklava
text:
Turkey claims to break Guinness world record for largest baklava Friday, March 23, 2018 - 00:59 
A team of 14 chefs have beaten the previous record for the largest baklava by over 300kg at an event in Ankara. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
